# Auto Push + Deploy (paperclip-vm / twcto_docker)

Production: **paperclip-vm** (`140.245.14.17`) running [bipulsin/twcto_docker](https://github.com/bipulsin/twcto_docker).

| Repo | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `bipulsin/trademanthan` | Application source (FastAPI, frontend, algos) |
| `bipulsin/twcto_docker` | Docker compose, Dockerfiles, deploy scripts, GHCR images |

After **app-affecting** changes in `/Users/bipulsahay/TradeManthan`, unless the user says not to deploy:

1. Commit and `git push origin main` on **trademanthan**.
2. Deploy on paperclip-vm:
   - **Preferred:** `REBUILD=1 ./scripts/trigger-paperclip-deploy.sh`
   - **Or one step:** `./scripts/release-push-and-deploy.sh -m "commit message"`
3. Verify: `curl -s https://www.tradewithcto.com/scan/health`

After **Docker/compose/nginx-in-container** changes, commit and push to **twcto_docker** `main`, then run `./scripts/trigger-paperclip-deploy.sh` (CI also publishes GHCR images on twcto_docker push).

Do **not** use retired EC2 (`3.6.199.247`) or `POST /scan/deploy-backend` (that path targeted EC2 systemd, not Docker).

SSH: `./scripts/paperclip-ssh.sh` or `ssh paperclip` — see `.cursor/rules/ec2-ssh.mdc`.
